\c 28
\s Izembatho zabapristi
\p
\v 1 Wena-ke sondeza kuwe uAroni umnewenu lamadodana akhe kanye laye\x + Nani 18.7. Heb. 5.4.\x*, phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli, ukuze bangisebenzele njengabapristi, uAroni, uNadabi loAbihu, uEleyazare loIthamari, amadodana kaAroni\x + 6.23; 24.1.\x*.
\v 2 Umenzele-ke uAroni umnewenu izembatho ezingcwele\x + 28.40.29.5,29; 31.10; 39.1,2. Levi 8.7,30. Nani 20.26,28.\x*, ezobukhosi lezokucecisa.
\v 3 Wena-ke khuluma labo bonke abahlakaniphileyo ngenhliziyo\x + 31.6; 35.10,25; 36.1.\x*, engibagcwalise ngomoya wenhlakanipho\x + 31.3; 35.30,31.\x*, ukuze benze izembatho zikaAroni zokumehlukanisela ukungisebenzela njengompristi.
\v 4 Lalezi yizembatho abazazenza; isembatho sesifuba\x + 28.15.\x* \w le-efodi\w**\x + 28.6.\x*, lebhatshi\x + 28.31.\x*, lesigqoko esilamabala\x + 28.39.\x*, iqhiye\x + 28.39.\x*, lebhanti\x + 28.39.\x*; bamenzele uAroni umnewenu izembatho ezingcwele, lezamadodana akhe, ukuze angisebenzele njengompristi.
\v 5 Bona-ke kabathathe igolide lokuluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka\x + 25.4; 28.6,8,15,39.\x* lokuyibubende lokubomvu lelembu elicolekileyo kakhulu.
\p
\v 6 Basebesenza i-efodi ngegolide\x + 28.14; 39.2-7.\x*, okuluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka\x + 25.4; 28.6,8,15,39.\x*, lokuyibubende, okubomvu, lelembu elicolekileyo lentambo ephothiweyo, umsebenzi wengcitshi\x + 26.1,31; 28.15.\x*.
\v 7 Sizakuba lezichibi ezimbili zamahlombe, zihlangane emaceleni aso womabili, ukuze sihlanganiswe.
\v 8 Ibhanti elelukwe ngobungcitshi le-efodi lakhe, elikuye, lizakuba njengomsebenzi walo, liyinto yinye, ngegolide, okuluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka\x + 25.4; 28.6,8,15,39.\x*, lokuyibubende, lokubomvu, lelembu elicolekileyo lentambo ephothiweyo.
\v 9 Njalo uzathatha amatshe amabili \w ama-onikse\w**\x + Gen. 2.12.\x*, ubaze kuwo amabizo amadodana kaIsrayeli,
\v 10 ayisithupha kumabizo awo phezu kwelinye ilitshe, lamabizo ayisithupha aseleyo phezu kwelinye ilitshe, njengokuzalwa kwawo.
\v 11 Njengomsebenzi wombazi wamatshe\x + 28.21.\x*, njengokubazwa kwendandatho elophawu, uzawabaza amatshe womabili, ngamabizo amadodana kaIsrayeli, uwenze amiswe ezisekelweni zegolide ezitshiliweyo.
\v 12 Njalo uzabeka amatshe womabili ezichibini zamahlombe \w ze-efodi\w**, amatshe esikhumbuzo ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli; loAroni uzathwala amabizo abo emahlombe akhe womabili phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 28.29,30.\x*\nd*, kube yisikhumbuzo\x + Nani 16.40. Josh. 4.7. Zek. 6.14.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Wenze lezisekelo ezitshiliweyo zegolide,
\v 14 lamaketane amabili egolide elicwengekileyo\x + 28.22,24,25; 39.15.\x*, uwenze ukuthi abe njengamagoda, umsebenzi ophothiweyo, amaketane aphothiweyo uwabophele ezisekelweni ezitshiliweyo zegolide.
\p
\v 15 Ubususenza isembatho sesifuba sokwahlulela\x + 28.28; 39.8-21.\x*, kube ngumsebenzi wengcitshi\x + 26.1.\x*, uyenze njengomsebenzi we-efodi, ngegolide, okuluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka\x + 25.4; 28.6,8,15,39.\x*, lokuyibubende, lokubomvu, langelembu elicolekileyo lentambo ephothiweyo uzasenza.
\v 16 Kasilingane inhlangothi zozine, siphindwe kabili, ubude baso bube yikwelulwa kweminwe, lobubanzi baso bube yikwelulwa kweminwe.
\v 17 Njalo uhlele kuso inhlelo zamatshe\x + Hez. 28.13. Isam. 21.19,20.\x*, imizila emine yamatshe; umzila \w wesardiyusi\w**, \w itopazi\w** \w le-emeraldi\w**, umzila wokuqala.
\v 18 lomzila wesibili ube \w lerubi\w**, \w isafire\w**, lendayimana\x + 24.10.\x*,
\v 19 lomzila wesithathu ube \w lejasinte\w**, \w i-agate\w**, \w le-ametiste\w**,
\v 20 lomzila wesine ube \w lebherule\w**, \w le-onikse\w**, \w lejaspi\w**; amatshe la azasekelwa ngegolide ezisekelweni zawo ezitshiliweyo.
\v 21 Lamatshe azakuba lamabizo amadodana kaIsrayeli, alitshumi lambili, lamabizo awo; njengokubazwa kwendandatho elophawu, yilelo lalelo lebizo lalo; azakuba ngawezizwe ezilitshumi lambili.
\p
\v 22 Wenze-ke esembathweni sesifuba amaketane aphothiweyo omsebenzi wegoda egolide elicwengekileyo,
\v 23 wenze futhi phezu kwesembatho sesifuba amasongo amabili egolide, uwafake amasongo amabili emaceleni womabili esembatho sesifuba.
\v 24 Ufake \add amaketane\add* amabili egolide aphothiweyo emasongweni amabili emaceleni esembatho sesifuba;
\v 25 kodwa izihloko zombili \add zamaketane\add* womabili aphothiweyo uzifake ezisekelweni ezimbili ezitshiliweyo, uzibeke ezichibini ze-efodi, phambili kwayo kanye.
\p
\v 26 Uzakwenza njalo amasongo amabili egolide, uwafake emaceleni womabili esembatho sesifuba, emphethweni waso ongaphakathi kwe-efodi.
\v 27 Wenze futhi amasongo amabili egolide, uwafake ezichibini ezimbili ze-efodi, ngaphansi ngaphambili kwaso, eduze kokuhlangana kwazo, phezu kwebhanti elelukwe ngobungcitshi le-efodi\x + 28.8.\x*.
\v 28 Bazabophela-ke isembatho sesifuba ngamasongo aso emasongweni e-efodi ngentambo eluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka, ukuze sibe phezu kwebhanti elelukwe ngobungcitshi\x + 28.8.\x*, njalo isembatho sesifuba singakhumuki e-efodini.
\v 29 Njalo uAroni uzathwala amabizo abantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 28.12,30.\x* esembathweni sesifuba sokwahlulela phezu kwenhliziyo yakhe, nxa engena e\add ndaw\add*eni engcwele, kube yisikhumbuzo phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* njalonjalo.
\p
\v 30 Uzafaka-ke esembathweni sesifuba sokwahlulela iUrimi leThumimi\x + Levi 8.8. Nani 27.21. Dute. 33.8. 1 Sam. 28.6. Ezra 2.63. Neh. 7.65. Levi 8.8. Nani 27.21. Dute. 33.8. 1 Sam. 28.6. Ezra 2.63. Neh. 7.65. 1 Sam. 23.9; 30.7.\x*, njalo kube phezu kwenhliziyo kaAroni, nxa engena phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*; ngakho uAroni uzakuthwala ukwahlulelwa kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli phezu kwenhliziyo yakhe phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* njalonjalo\x + 28.29.\x*.
\p
\v 31 Uzakwenza ibhatshi lonke le-efodi ngokuluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka\x + 28.37; 39.22-31.28.4.\x*;
\v 32 njalo sibe lesikhala sekhanda ngaphakathi kwaso, isikhala sibe lomphetho osizingelezeleyo, umsebenzi owelukiweyo, sibe njengesikhala sebhatshi lensimbi, ukuze singadabuki\x + Joha. 19.23.\x*.
\p
\v 33 Lemiphethweni yaso wenze \w amapomegranati\w** ngokuluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka lokuyibubende lokubomvu, emiphethweni yaso osizingelezeleyo, lamabhera egolide phakathi kwawo asizingelezeleyo,
\v 34 ibhera legolide lepomegranati, ibhera legolide lepomegranati, emiphethweni yebhatshi kuzingelezele.
\v 35 UAroni kasembathele-ke ukukhonza, lokukhenceza kwaso kuzwakale lapho engena e\add ndaw\add*eni engcwele phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, lalapho ephuma, ukuze angafi.
\p
\v 36 Uzakwenza njalo incence ngegolide elicwengekileyo\x + Levi 8.9. Zek. 14.20.\x*, ubaze kuyo ukubazwa kwendandatho elophawu\x + 28.21.\x*: UBUNGCWELE ENKOSINI\x + 15.11.\x*.
\v 37 Uyifake phezu kwentambo eluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka, ukuze ibe phezu kweqhiye\x + 28.4.\x*, ibe ngaphambili kweqhiye.
\v 38 Izakuba sebunzini likaAroni, ukuze uAroni athwale ububi bezinto ezingcwele\x + Levi 10.17. Nani 18.1. Levi 22.9. Isa. 53.11. Hez. 4.4,5,6. Joha. 1.29. Heb. 9.28. 1 Pet. 2.24.28.43.\x*, abantwana bakoIsrayeli abazazingcwelisa, kuzo zonke izipho zabo ezingcwele; njalo izahlala isebunzini lakhe, ukuze bemukeleke phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + Levi 1.4; 22.27; 23.11; Isa. 56.7.\x*\nd*.
\p
\v 39 Uzakweluka njalo isigqoko ngelembu elicolekileyo kakhulu elilamabala\x + 28.4,5.\x*, wenze leqhiye ngelembu elicolekileyo kakhulu, lebhanti, umsebenzi womfekethisi ngenalithi\x + 26.36.\x*.
\p
\v 40 Wenzele-ke amadodana kaAroni\x + 39.27,28,29,41; Hez. 44.17,18.\x* izigqoko, uwenzele amabhanti\x + 28.4,5.\x*, lezingowane uwenzele, kube ngokobukhosi lokuceca\x + 28.2.\x*.
\v 41 Umgqokise zona uAroni umnewenu lamadodana akhe kanye laye, ubagcobe\x + 29.7; 30.30; 40.15. Levi 10.7.\x*, ubehlukanise, ubangcwelise ukuze bangisebenzele njengabapristi.
\v 42 Ubenzele labokabhudula bangaphansi belembu elicolekileyo\x + 39.28. Levi 6.10; 16.4. Hez. 44.18.\x* okusibekela inyama yobunqunu, aqale ekhalweni afike emathangazini;
\v 43 njalo uAroni lamadodana akhe bawagqoke lapho bengena ethenteni lenhlangano kumbe lapho besondela elathini ukukhonza e\add ndaw\add*eni engcwele\x + 20.26.\x*, hlezi bathwale ububi\x + Levi 5.1,17; 20.19.\x*, bafe. \add Kuzakuba\add* yisimiso esilaphakade\x + 27.21.\x* kuye lakuyo inzalo yakhe emva kwakhe.
